# Laravel Backend Architecture - /app Directory

## Overview

The backend implements a sophisticated business process management and assessment system using Laravel 12 with modern PHP 8.2+ features. The architecture follows Domain-Driven Design principles with clear separation of concerns.

## Directory Structure

```
app/
