```

#### Key Models

**BusinessProcessCore** (`app/Models/BusinessProcessCore.php`)
- Central model for process instances
- Manages SOP, RACI, Visual, Swimlane content through polymorphic relations
- Handles version control for all content types
- Implements user ownership and access control

**BusinessProcessActivity** (`app/Models/BusinessProcessActivity.php`)
- Individual process activities with RACI assignments
- Drag-and-drop position management
- Relationships to blueprints for detailed instructions
- JSON fields for flexible RACI data storage

### 2. Assessment System

#### Core Assessment Models

**AssessmentTemplate** (`app/Models/AssessmentTemplate.php`)
- Assessment configurations and metadata
- Soft deletes for template management
- Industry-specific configurations (NAICS)
- Admin-only management with feature flags

**UserAssessment** (`app/Models/UserAssessment.php`)
- User's assessment instances
- Progress tracking and completion status
- Data storage in JSON fields for flexibility
- Relationship to assessment progress tracking

**UserAssessmentProgress** (`app/Models/UserAssessmentProgress.php`)
- Granular progress tracking
- Question-level completion status
- Review flagging system
- Performance analytics data

#### Assessment Questions System

**AssessmentQuestion** (`app/Models/AssessmentQuestion.php`)
- Dynamic question definitions
- Multiple question types (MCQ, NUMBER, TEXT, etc.)
- Conditional logic and dependencies
- Validation rules and constraints

## Controllers Architecture

### RESTful Resource Controllers

**BusinessProcessController** (`app/Http/Controllers/BusinessProcessController.php`)
- Main dashboard and process listing
- Statistics and analytics
- User-specific process filtering

**CoreProcessController** (`app/Http/Controllers/CoreProcessController.php`)
- Process core management (CRUD)
