## Database Relationships

### Complex Relationships

**Polymorphic Content System**
```php
// BusinessProcessCore has polymorphic content
public function contents()
{
    return $this->hasMany(BusinessProcessContent::class, 'core_id');
}

public function sopContent()
{
    return $this->contents()->where('type', 'sop')->latest()->first();
}

public function visualContent()  
{
    return $this->contents()->where('type', 'visual')->latest()->first();
}
```

**Assessment System Relationships**
```php
// User â†’ UserAssessment â†’ AssessmentTemplate â†’ AssessmentQuestion
// User â†’ UserAssessmentProgress â†’ AssessmentQuestion

class User extends Model
{
    public function assessments()
    {
        return $this->hasMany(UserAssessment::class);
    }

    public function assessmentProgress()
    {
        return $this->hasMany(UserAssessmentProgress::class);
    }

